## Release Notes

### Balancing

- Added money on defeating an enemy as incentive to actually defeat them

### Improvements

- Improved money pickup animation
- Added soundeffect when advancing a textbox
- Small improvement to titlescreen
- Changes to the music

### Bugs

- Fixed bug where the enemy ship on the titlescreen was moving to far

## Files included

- `void-merchants.p8` — PICO-8 standard cart in clear text format (Source code)
- `void-merchants.p8.png` — PICO-8 cart image
- `void-merchants_linux.zip` — Linux binaries
- `void-merchants_windows.zip` — Windows binaries
- `void-merchants_raspi.zip` — Raspberry Pi binaries
- `void-merchants_osx.zip` — macOS binaries
- `manual.pdf` — Manual for this release
- `LICENSE.txt` — Licensing information